The study utilized both quantitative and qualitative methods, as detailed in Figure 2. The study model was initially developed using information gathered from the literature review of previous research studies. Subsequently, in-depth interviews were conducted to validate the important factors in the proposed model and enhance the questionnaire framework for an upcoming survey, aiming to ensure its suitability within the context of recruitment in Thailand.
